title: Neek Lurk of Anti Social Social Club Releases "SPEEDING THRU YOU"

organizations.name: neek lurk of anti social social club

text:
http://hypebeast.com/2017/1/neek-lurk-speeding-thru-you?utm_source=link&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=share+buttons 
After releasing a music video last month, Neek Lurk of Anti Social Social Club recently took to Instagram to announce the drop of his latest track. “SPEEDING THRU YOU” from the presiding general of melancholia is a moody bass heavy ballad about regrets and longing. The track is the latest in the string of musical releases from Neek under the mysterious Foreshadow Records label. Listen to the track below and let us know what you think about Neek moving in the music realm.
